== Interfaces ==

ParallelismManagement.h : ParallelismManagement

DistributionLibrary.h : Internals API: DistributionLibrary, DistributionLibraryClient, DistributionLibraryServer

BasicBC.h		  : Exposed to Used

BasicBC_Redist.h	  : Internal

VectorAdd.h		  : User interface (va/uva)
VectorAdd_BC.h	  : Internal (vai/uvai)

== Components == 

BasicBC/		  : Internal, 2 components BasicBC_Client (provides: bcc, dlc, bc / uses: srcTopo, dstTopo)
			    	      		   BasicBC_Server (provides: bcs, dls, bc / uses: srcTopo, dstTopo) ** MEMCPY **

ParallelismManager/	  : Internal (provides: rank, size, pm / uses: rank, size)

BasicBC_Vector_Client/		: User Client component (provides: go, cc / uses: DUMP, N, BSZ, upm, ubc, uva)
BasicBC_Vector_Server/		: User Server component (provides: cc, va / uses: DUMP, upm, ubc)

BasicBC_Vector_Redist_Client/	: Internal (provides: cc, va  / uses: srcTopo, dstTopo, upm, ubc, udlc, uvai)
BasicBC_Vector_Redist_Client2/	: Internal (provides: cc, va  / uses: srcTopo, dstTopo, upm, ubc, udlc, uvai2)
BasicBC_Vector_Redist_Server/	: Internal (provides: cc, vai / uses: srcTopo, dstTopo, upm, ubc, udls, uva)

CcmLLCMMxNBlockSend/		: Internal (provides: vai2 / uses multiple CCM)
CcmLLCMMxNBlockReceive/		: Internal (provides: vai2 / uses multiple CCM)

BasicBC_Test/
